{"obj_edit_time":"1724313191","blocks":[{"block_id":"QWbfdDOScoMKi8xVUCUcayPFnIW","block_type":1,"children":["FaerdhhnLodkSaxJpfNcdFmwnVR","IqJKdKRMXoqGmqxI5UIcM8Llnvc","Pfmnd7qTSoBnigxjQJzcnbW5n8f"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"業務介紹","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"FaerdhhnLodkSaxJpfNcdFmwnVR","block_type":2,"parent_id":"QWbfdDOScoMKi8xVUCUcayPFnIW","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"Margin Call（追加保證金通知）作為一種券商的風險管理策略。指當交易者在利用槓桿的情況下，因部位虧損而導致保證金金額已經低於經紀商要求的保證金水平，或者說因市場波動而下跌至低於維持保證金水平時，券商就會向交易者發出Margin Call。在收到Margin Call後，交易者需及時（一般要求為3個交易日內）自行平倉，或是向其保證金賬戶注資，直到保證金賬戶金額回到券商要求的保證金水平，否則券商有權替客戶進行平倉，而無須事先通知。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"IqJKdKRMXoqGmqxI5UIcM8Llnvc","block_type":2,"parent_id":"QWbfdDOScoMKi8xVUCUcayPFnIW","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"Pfmnd7qTSoBnigxjQJzcnbW5n8f","block_type":2,"parent_id":"QWbfdDOScoMKi8xVUCUcayPFnIW","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}}]}